About Canada eCoin

Canada eCoin (CDN) is a cryptocurrency. Users are able to generate CDN through the process of mining. Canada eCoin has a current supply of 97,415,544 CDN. The last known price of Canada eCoin is 0.003037 USD and is up 12.52% over the last 24 hours. It is currently trading on 2 active market(s) with 13 USD traded over the last 24 hours. More information can be found at http://www.canadaecoin.ca/.
